"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Iran's Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi says the country has not asked for a ceasefire, despite Trump's claim that Iran wanted a deal.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran Denies Ceasefire Request\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Ministro de Relaciones Exteriores de Ir\u00e1n, Abbas Araghchi, dice que el pa\u00eds no ha pedido un alto al fuego, a pesar de que Trump dice que Ir\u00e1n quer\u00eda un acuerdo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ir\u00e1n Niega Pedir Alto al Fuego\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The war-torn country is trying to get important funding from the IMF and EU, and is also raising taxes.\",            \"english_title\": \"Country Seeks Funding\",            \"translated_version\": \"El pa\u00eds en guerra est\u00e1 tratando de obtener dinero importante del FMI y la UE, y tambi\u00e9n est\u00e1 subiendo los impuestos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pa\u00eds Busca Dinero\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Volodymyr Zelensky says that allowing Russian oil to flow through Ukraine to the EU would be like lifting sanctions on Russia.\",            \"english_title\": \"Zelensky on Russian Oil\",            \"translated_version\": \"Volodymyr Zelensky dice que permitir que el petr\u00f3leo ruso pase por Ucrania hacia la UE ser\u00eda como quitar las sanciones a Rusia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Zelensky sobre Petr\u00f3leo Ruso\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Five of the seven members of the women's football delegation who wanted to stay in Australia have decided to go back home. Prosecutors say a loaded gun, hydrochloric acid, and an Islamic State flag were found in their car.\",            \"english_title\": \"Football Delegation Returns\",            \"translated_version\": \"Cinco de los siete miembros de la delegaci\u00f3n de f\u00fatbol femenino que quer\u00edan quedarse en Australia han decidido regresar a casa. Los fiscales dicen que encontraron un arma cargada, \u00e1cido clorh\u00eddrico y una bandera del Estado Isl\u00e1mico en su coche.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Delegaci\u00f3n de F\u00fatbol Regresa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Discontent is growing over ongoing blackouts and shortages of food, fuel, and medicine, made worse by a US blockade.\",            \"english_title\": \"Growing Discontent\",            \"translated_version\": \"El descontento est\u00e1 creciendo por los apagones continuos y la falta de comida, combustible y medicinas, empeorado por un bloqueo de EE.UU.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Descontento Creciente\"        }    ]}"